translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_435c0476:

    # yu "Hezz, how's the tribe going lately?"
    yu "长老，最近我们部落怎么样？"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_f876c6af:

    # hz "Well, we're doing fine. The harvest is good this year, and we have enough food to last us through the winter."
    hz "嗯～井然有序。今年收成挺好的，不愁过冬没东西吃。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_1143a178:

    # hz "But, we're still missing Chime, and that's a big problem."
    hz "但齐门失踪了，这件事很严重。毕竟他不是一声不吭就离家出走的孩子。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_40f93814:

    # hz "Afterall, he is not one who wanders off without telling anyone."
    pass

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_849afa84:

    # hz "Shudo and Pairon were worried pant-less, especially after you told them you had to get in the forest by yourself."
    hz "就算你要独自进入森林也会先告诉舒笃和帕里恩，可把他们担心坏了。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_00f15793:

    # yu "I'm sorry Hezz, I didn't mean to worry them. But they know I will keep searching while they rest."
    yu "对不起长老，我不是故意要他们担心的，我只是想让他们知道他们休息的时候还有我在找。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_dffae502:

    # hz "Hmm, don't worry about it, I will tell them you're safe when you come back."
    hz "没事，等你明天早上回来我会告诉他们你一切安好。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_1a1af4f3:

    # hz "Look, we are not a big tribe, we need to look for each other's back, especially in times like this."
    hz "哎……普罗是个小部落，需要大家相互扶持、相互照顾，特别是现在这种时候。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_6df21e82:

    # yu "I know, I know. I just want to find Chime and bring him back."
    yu "我懂，我懂。但一想到齐门可能有危险，要我怎么坐得住。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_bc7e7f02:

    # hz "You know, I'm worried about you too. You haven't slept for a week, and you look like a mess."
    hz "其实我也很担心你。你这一周都没怎么睡过，现在看起来多憔悴。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_0d58f772:

    # "You look down at your feet, maybe he's right, but what is the alternative... do you just give up on the search."
    "你低头看着自己的脚，长老或许是对的，但你还有什么选择……难道就这么放弃了？"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_3feb7cac:

    # "You don't ever want to think about living in a world without your best friend, even at the cost of wearing out your body bit by bit."
    "你不愿想象失去人生挚友的生活，即使搜救的劳累日复一日啃食你的身体。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_2748387b:

    # yu "Would he be okay? I mean, if I don't find him now, what's the chance of him... ever coming back."
    yu "如果我不尽快找到他，那他……还会回来吗？他还活着吗？"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_c7424302:

    # hz "I- uh... Well."
    hz "这……"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_06aee3a8:

    # hz "I will be honest with you, the chance is only getting lower and lower as time passes."
    hz "实话实说，他平安归来的概率每天都在变小。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_0ba95c65:

    # hz "But we aren't giving up on him, our search party hasn't stopped yet, and we will keep looking for him."
    hz "但这不是放弃的理由，我们的搜救队还没解散，我们一定会继续找下去的。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_591f9294:

    # yu "Okay."
    yu "嗯……"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_3aaf063d:

    # yu "Hezz, do you know why... Chime's missing?"
    yu "长老，你觉得……齐门为什么会不见呢？"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_56f3617b:

    # hz "There is no way I can know, but I have a feeling that it's not a good sign."
    hz "我也没有头绪，但我预感不妙。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_4a280ab3:

    # yu "Why are you saying that?"
    yu "为什么呢？"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_c014d137:

    # hz "I only just recalled now, but the day before he went missing, he told me about a pair of eyes while we were hunting."
    hz "我才想起来，他失踪的前一天我们在一起打猎，他说有一双眼睛盯着他。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_bb469eb3:

    # hz "He said there were horns behind the eyes, and it was staring at him from the bushes."
    hz "透过树丛可以隐约看到那个身影长着角。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_79d0db84:

    # hz "I didn't think much of it at the time, so I told him, well. Maybe it's your friend messing with you."
    hz "我没想那么多，就告诉他可能是哪个朋友跟他闹着玩呢。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_0a14b3ae:

    # hz "But now that I think of it, it's a little worrying."
    hz "现在回想起来齐门那天的话，是有点蹊跷。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_28acdb1d:

    # yu "Hezz, couldn't you have told me this earlier?"
    yu "这么重要的事情怎么之前不告诉我？"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_3c97bf31:

    # hz "I didn't think it was important... I thought it was you or someone else, after all, horns aren't something rare in our tribe."
    hz "放在当时谁会觉得重要……我还以为那个人是你还是谁，毕竟我们部落谁不长角。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_8182700b:

    # yu "W-what if he's kidnapped by that pair of eyes?"
    yu "难道——齐门被那个人绑架了？"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_67f51c85:

    # hz "Or, it can still be something else innocent, and uhm... he just got lost in the forest."
    hz "或者，那个人不过是个无辜的过路人，齐门只是呃……单纯在森林里迷路了。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_dad363b4:

    # yu "After you told me this, I'm not sure if I can believe he {i}just{/i} got lost."
    yu "知道这档事之后要我怎么相信齐门只是“单纯”地迷路。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_e5689667:

    # hz "Maybe you are right."
    hz "迷路、绑架，都有可能。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_0e5be6e7:

    # hz "Didn't you mention having seen a glowing light somewhere?"
    hz "对了，你之前说晚上看到哪有亮光？"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_1c496b36:

    # yu "I thought it was Chime, but I'm not sure now."
    yu "我以为那是齐门，但现在我又不确定了。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_3fa769d8:

    # hz "Well, maybe it's someone else's."
    hz "嗯，可能是别人搞出的什么事情。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_6cb3fe54:

    # hz "If he's kidnapped, then we have to track that person down, somehow. But we have no trails to start off of."
    hz "假如齐门被绑架了，我们不管怎样肯定要把那个人找出来，可惜我们连一点开头的线索都没有。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_3ac77472:

    # yu "You're right."
    yu "好吧。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_f27be97b:

    # yu "Hezz, what do I need to do as a watcher?"
    yu "长老，守夜人一般要做些什么呢？"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_2616a8b3:

    # hz "Well, as a normal watcher, you just need to keep the tribe safe at night, and alert us if anything suspicious happen."
    hz "咳，守夜人负责维护部落夜里的安全，如果有异常情况及时向大家发出警报。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_48711521:

    # hz "Usually, we assign two watchers every night to perform this job, but they don't seem to be available tonight."
    hz "通常会有两个人搭班，今天属于特殊情况。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_ff260648:

    # hz "It's a routine job, but it's important. You know, we don't want those sprites to come in and steal our food."
    hz "虽然这是按部就班的常规工作，但不能因此松懈怠慢。你也不想那些幽魂再进来偷走我们的粮食了，对吧。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_bff81938:

    # yu "What should I do if I see one?"
    yu "假如我碰到幽魂了该怎么办？"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_3de55463:

    # hz "Fight, of course. You have a sword, right?"
    hz "当然是消灭它，就用你带的这把剑。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_ec9559e5:

    # yu "Yes, I do. But it's not very sharp."
    yu "但这把剑已经有点钝了。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_9455fb67:

    # hz "It's fine, it's not like you're going to fight a demon or something."
    hz "没关系，又不是派你去打恶魔或者什么危险的魔兽。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_056070d0:

    # yu "Well I hope not."
    yu "希望真不是吧。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_6294513b:

    # hz "If you lost your sword, just raise your arm, puff out your chest and make a loud noise. These sprites are not very brave, they will scramble at the slightest bit of sound."
    hz "如果你的剑掉了，记得立马张开双臂，屏气挺胸，然后大叫。幽魂比较胆小，搞出点声响就能把他们吓跑。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_8f256263:

    # "Hezzong demonstrates as he pulls his shoulders back, showing off his huge chest muscles in confidence."
    "赫宗两肩后张，秀出他宽厚的胸肌，将动作演示给你。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_2d9914e4:

    # hz "See, that's pretty easy."
    hz "就像这样，非常简单。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_53f672c4:

    # "He smirks at your blushed gaze, obviously proud of his act having an opposite effect on you."
    "看着你不好意思却又目不转睛的样子，大长老露出了得意的笑容。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_ab555e41:

    # yu "Well..."
    yu "哈……"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_e74dbc3c:

    # yu "Who are those sprites, actually?"
    yu "那这些幽魂究竟是什么东西？"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_e7bfe6a1:

    # "The elder shrugs, returning to his normal position, but his chest is still puffed out."
    "大长老耸耸肩，恢复了自然的姿态，但那对雄峰依然十分饱满。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_5759bab5:

    # hz "Wandering pests, nothing more. They are not dangerous, but they can be annoying."
    hz "它们就像游荡荒野的小害虫，没什么危险性，但可以很烦人，仅此而已。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_a7cf4b21:

    # yu "I see."
    yu "我明白了。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_ab851ef2:

    # yu "You know, I haven't seen one before, so it's all new to me."
    yu "唔，我还没见过幽魂长什么样，这些事情我还是第一次接触。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_d95b16c5:

    # hz "That's because the watchers are doing their job. Wouldn't you prefer that?"
    hz "说明之前的守夜人工作做到位了，才没让你“有机会”见到幽魂。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_738a31d1:

    # yu "You are right, allfather."
    yu "好像是这个理。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_ddd1348d:

    # yu "Hezz, maybe I need to take a breather tomorrow."
    yu "长老，明天我想请假。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_98d82c67:

    # hz "What? Why?"
    hz "噢？为什么？"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_162406f0:

    # yu "I- I am still looking for Chime, just need some extra time to sleep."
    yu "为、为了找齐门，我需要多补一会觉。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_80ba5239:

    # hz "You know, I can't do all the work by myself, right?"
    hz "你也知道，我一个人没法干完这么多活，嗯？"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_f5c54ff4:

    # yu "Yeah, but you did, last time I checked you finished all the books and accounts by yourself while I was away."
    yu "才怪，上回我出去的时候你就一个人理完了所有台账。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_0f4867aa:

    # hz "But I can't finish all of these all the time, that's why I hired you."
    hz "但我不可能每天都保质保量完成所有工作，所以才雇了你当助手啊。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_554c38e4:

    # yu "But you did! You are perfectly capable to do so."
    yu "但长老你已经证明了你可以！完全可以！"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_e5ae3808:

    # hz "Yeah, you're right."
    hz "哎，你要硬犟这点我也没办法。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_c6533285:

    # hz "Hey, how about this, I'll be honest with you. I care more about you than the ever-stacking books, I just want to keep you around while you're looking for Chime."
    hz "不妨直说，我真正关心的是你，而不是那堆越摞越高的本子。我只是不想你因为找齐门离我太远。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_b4404d94:

    # hz "Perhaps, you can use my bed if you happen to be tired after the post. It's the closest from the tower, and I can keep an eye on you."
    hz "守完夜困的话可以睡我的床，离瞭望塔最近不用走远路，也方便我照看你。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_83da2bb5:

    # hz "And, I will make sure you get those extra sleep tomorrow. No need to worry about the books."
    hz "所以明天你就安心补觉，不用操心台账。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_eb4d3c79:

    # yu "Really? Thank you, Hezzong."
    yu "真的吗？谢谢长老。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_c0483b72:

    # hz "I hope you don't mind sharing a bed with an old white-bearded dragon, or having to make it through my snores."
    hz "但愿你不介意和一个胡子花白的老龙一张床，还有我的呼噜。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_82c2724d:

    # hz "I will try to keep it down, but I can't promise anything."
    hz "我会想办法尽量小声点，但不保证效果哈。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_a11ed5ff:

    # yu "You're my allfather afterall, of course I don't mind. I'm already grateful to have a warm bed."
    yu "你可是我的天父，我当然不介意。能有一张暖床钻我已经很感激了。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_4973b1f6:

    # hz "Good, then it's settled."
    hz "好，那就愉快地决定了。"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_126c5452:

    # yu "Hezzong, what should I do right now?"
    yu "长老，我现在要做什么？"

translate schinese Hezzong_Puro_Forest_Dialogue_72969426:

    # hz "Just try to take a look at the crate over there."
    hz "去检查一下那边的木箱。"

